===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Cynthia (Masters)}}
Cynthia forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Cynthia|Garchomp}}, {{p|Kommo-o}}, {{fd|Giratina|Altered Forme}} {{p|Giratina}}, {{fd|Gastrodon|West Sea}} {{p|Gastrodon}}, {{p|Lucario}}, {{p|Spiritomb}}, and {{p|Milotic}} in {{g|Masters EX}}. Both her Garchomp and Lucario are capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Cynthia became a playable sync pair on January 1, 2020.

Cynthia first appeared as an NPC during the first chapter of [[PML arc]]. She also made notable appearances later in the PML arc, [[Legendary Adventures]], and the [[villain arc]].

